vars: {
  d2-config: {
    layout-engine: elk
    theme-id: 4
  }
}
direction: down
title: |md
  ## HTTP/1.1 Request Wire Format — Annotated Byte Map
  `GET /index.html HTTP/1.1\r\nHost: localhost:8080\r\nUser-Agent: curl/7.88.1\r\nAccept: */*\r\n\r\n`
| {near: top-center}
classes: {
  method_field: {
    style: {
      fill: "#7B2FBE"
      font-color: white
      bold: true
      border-radius: 2
    }
  }
  path_field: {
    style: {
      fill: "#1565C0"
      font-color: white
      bold: true
      border-radius: 2
    }
  }
  version_field: {
    style: {
      fill: "#0277BD"
      font-color: white
      bold: true
      border-radius: 2
    }
  }
  header_name: {
    style: {
      fill: "#2E7D32"
      font-color: white
      bold: true
      border-radius: 2
    }
  }
  header_value: {
    style: {
      fill: "#1565C0"
      font-color: white
      border-radius: 2
    }
  }
  delimiter: {
    style: {
      fill: "#B71C1C"
      font-color: white
      bold: true
      border-radius: 2
    }
  }
  separator: {
    style: {
      fill: "#E65100"
      font-color: white
      bold: true
      border-radius: 2
    }
  }
  padding_field: {
    style: {
      fill: "#616161"
      font-color: white
      border-radius: 2
    }
  }
  region_label: {
    style: {
      fill: transparent
      stroke: transparent
      bold: true
      font-size: 13
    }
  }
  zone_box: {
    style: {
      border-radius: 6
      stroke-width: 2
    }
  }
}
request_line_zone: "parse_request_line() consumes — bytes [0..25]" {
  class: zone_box
  style: {
    fill: "#F3E5F5"
    stroke: "#7B2FBE"
    stroke-width: 2
  }
  row0: {
    style: {
      fill: transparent
      stroke: transparent
    }
    grid-columns: 10
    grid-gap: 3
    b0: "G\n[0]" { class: method_field; width: 52; height: 52 }
    b1: "E\n[1]" { class: method_field; width: 52; height: 52 }
    b2: "T\n[2]" { class: method_field; width: 52; height: 52 }
    b3: "SP\n[3]" { class: separator; width: 52; height: 52 }
    b4: "/in…\n[4..14]" { class: path_field; width: 90; height: 52 }
    b5: "SP\n[15]" { class: separator; width: 52; height: 52 }
    b6: "HTTP/1.1\n[16..23]" { class: version_field; width: 90; height: 52 }
    b7: "CR\n[24]" { class: delimiter; width: 52; height: 52 }
    b8: "LF\n[25]" { class: delimiter; width: 52; height: 52 }
    b9: "← CRLF\nterminates\nrequest line" {
      style: {
        fill: transparent
        stroke: transparent
        font-color: "#B71C1C"
        italic: true
        font-size: 11
      }
      width: 110
      height: 52
    }
  }
  legend0: |md
    **method** `GET` = bytes 0–2 (3 B) · **SP** = byte 3 (0x20) · **path** `/index.html` = bytes 4–14 (11 B) · **SP** = byte 15 · **version** `HTTP/1.1` = bytes 16–23 (8 B) · **CRLF** = bytes 24–25
  | {
    style: {
      fill: transparent
      stroke: transparent
      font-size: 11
    }
  }
}
host_header_zone: "parse_headers() — Header 1: Host (bytes 26..49)" {
  class: zone_box
  style: {
    fill: "#E8F5E9"
    stroke: "#2E7D32"
    stroke-width: 2
  }
  row1: {
    style: {
      fill: transparent
      stroke: transparent
    }
    grid-columns: 9
    grid-gap: 3
    h1n: "Host\n[26..29]" { class: header_name; width: 68; height: 52 }
    h1c: ":\n[30]" { class: separator; width: 36; height: 52 }
    h1s: "SP\n[31]" { class: padding_field; width: 36; height: 52 }
    h1v: "localhost:8080\n[32..45]" { class: header_value; width: 130; height: 52 }
    h1cr: "CR\n[46]" { class: delimiter; width: 36; height: 52 }
    h1lf: "LF\n[47]" { class: delimiter; width: 36; height: 52 }
    h1ann: "← name(4B) : OWS(1B) value(14B) CRLF" {
      style: {
        fill: transparent
        stroke: transparent
        italic: true
        font-color: "#2E7D32"
        font-size: 11
      }
      width: 220
      height: 52
    }
  }
}
ua_header_zone: "parse_headers() — Header 2: User-Agent (bytes 48..72)" {
  class: zone_box
  style: {
    fill: "#E8F5E9"
    stroke: "#2E7D32"
    stroke-width: 2
  }
  row2: {
    style: {
      fill: transparent
      stroke: transparent
    }
    grid-columns: 9
    grid-gap: 3
    h2n: "User-Agent\n[48..57]" { class: header_name; width: 100; height: 52 }
    h2c: ":\n[58]" { class: separator; width: 36; height: 52 }
    h2s: "SP\n[59]" { class: padding_field; width: 36; height: 52 }
    h2v: "curl/7.88.1\n[60..70]" { class: header_value; width: 100; height: 52 }
    h2cr: "CR\n[71]" { class: delimiter; width: 36; height: 52 }
    h2lf: "LF\n[72]" { class: delimiter; width: 36; height: 52 }
    h2ann: "← name(10B) : OWS(1B) value(11B) CRLF" {
      style: {
        fill: transparent
        stroke: transparent
        italic: true
        font-color: "#2E7D32"
        font-size: 11
      }
      width: 220
      height: 52
    }
  }
}
accept_header_zone: "parse_headers() — Header 3: Accept (bytes 73..86)" {
  class: zone_box
  style: {
    fill: "#E8F5E9"
    stroke: "#2E7D32"
    stroke-width: 2
  }
  row3: {
    style: {
      fill: transparent
      stroke: transparent
    }
    grid-columns: 9
    grid-gap: 3
    h3n: "Accept\n[73..78]" { class: header_name; width: 80; height: 52 }
    h3c: ":\n[79]" { class: separator; width: 36; height: 52 }
    h3s: "SP\n[80]" { class: padding_field; width: 36; height: 52 }
    h3v: "*/*\n[81..83]" { class: header_value; width: 64; height: 52 }
    h3cr: "CR\n[84]" { class: delimiter; width: 36; height: 52 }
    h3lf: "LF\n[85]" { class: delimiter; width: 36; height: 52 }
    h3ann: "← name(6B) : OWS(1B) value(3B) CRLF" {
      style: {
        fill: transparent
        stroke: transparent
        italic: true
        font-color: "#2E7D32"
        font-size: 11
      }
      width: 220
      height: 52
    }
  }
}
empty_line_zone: "parse_headers() — Empty Line = End-of-Headers Sentinel (bytes 86..87)" {
  class: zone_box
  style: {
    fill: "#FFEBEE"
    stroke: "#B71C1C"
    stroke-width: 3
  }
  row4: {
    style: {
      fill: transparent
      stroke: transparent
    }
    grid-columns: 5
    grid-gap: 3
    e0: "CR\n[86]" { class: delimiter; width: 64; height: 52 }
    e1: "LF\n[87]" { class: delimiter; width: 64; height: 52 }
    eann: |md
      **`\r\n\r\n`** = bytes 85–87 (last CRLF of Accept header + this empty CRLF)
      `strstr(buf, "\r\n\r\n")` matches here → `read_request()` returns
      `req->body` pointer set to byte 88 (first byte after empty line)
    | {
      style: {
        fill: transparent
        stroke: transparent
        font-size: 11
        font-color: "#B71C1C"
      }
      width: 500
      height: 52
    }
  }
}
body_zone: "Body region (byte 88+) — empty for GET; req->body_len = 0" {
  class: zone_box
  style: {
    fill: "#E3F2FD"
    stroke: "#1565C0"
    stroke-dash: 4
  }
  label_body: "No body bytes follow for GET request.\nFor POST: Content-Length header specifies byte count; body starts at byte 88." {
    style: {
      fill: transparent
      stroke: transparent
      font-size: 11
      italic: true
    }
  }
}
color_legend: "Color Legend" {
  style: {
    fill: "#FAFAFA"
    stroke: "#9E9E9E"
    border-radius: 6
    font-size: 12
  }
  grid-columns: 3
  grid-gap: 8
  lm: "METHOD bytes" { class: method_field; width: 120; height: 32 }
  lp: "PATH bytes" { class: path_field; width: 120; height: 32 }
  lv: "VERSION bytes" { class: version_field; width: 120; height: 32 }
  lhn: "header-name" { class: header_name; width: 120; height: 32 }
  lhv: "header-value" { class: header_value; width: 120; height: 32 }
  ld: "CR / LF delimiter" { class: delimiter; width: 120; height: 32 }
  ls: "SP / colon separator" { class: separator; width: 120; height: 32 }
  lows: "OWS (optional whitespace)" { class: padding_field; width: 140; height: 32 }
}
size_annotation: |md
  **Total request size:** 88 bytes (26 request-line + 22 Host-hdr + 25 UA-hdr + 13 Accept-hdr + 2 empty-line)
  **`parse_request_line()`** receives `line_len = 24` (bytes 0–23, `\r` stripped, `\n` not included)
  **`parse_headers()`** begins scanning at byte 26 (first byte after request-line `\n`)
  **`get_header(req, "host")`** returns pointer to `"localhost:8080"` inside `req->headers[0].value`
| {
  near: bottom-center
  style: {
    fill: "#FFF9C4"
    stroke: "#F9A825"
    border-radius: 6
    font-size: 12
  }
}